#hm-note[
  Month 8 is the most inward-facing month of the entire second year. Laboratory
  work continues, but the primary pedagogical focus is the body as alchemical
  instrument. Some students will find this month revelatory; others will resist
  it as too psychological. The resistance itself is worth noting — it often
  indicates exactly the area where the deepest work is needed. Avoid
  psychologizing the tradition; keep the language alchemical. The body-awareness
  practice and Threefold Breath revision are the core deliverables.
]

